SECTION 11: Toxicological information
11.1 Information on toxicological effects
Mixture
Acute toxicity
Symptoms: Irritations of mucous membranes in the mouth, pharynx, oesophagus and
gastrointestinal tract.
Inhalation: No data available
Acute toxicity estimate Inhalation - 4 h - 75.71 mg/l - vapor(Calculation method)
Symptoms: Possible symptoms:, mucosal irritations
Dermal: No data available
Skin corrosion/irritation
Mixture causes skin irritation.
Serious eye damage/eye irritation
Mixture causes serious eye damage.
